Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.97,0:03:20.97,Takagi san—Picture 05-1,,0,0,0,,{\frz269.2\pos(1744,532)}讨厌的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:27.98,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么了  突然叹起气来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:29.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.96,0:03:31.93,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是因为早餐里有…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:40.54,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不  不知为何从早上开始就不在状态
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:44.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我说  早餐里有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.13,0:03:46.98,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.17,0:03:49.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:52.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好危险
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.05,0:03:58.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,如果让她知道我心情不好的原因是早饭里放了很多我讨厌的青椒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.74,0:04:03.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,原来你讨厌青椒啊  像个小孩一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:05.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,绝不能让她知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:07.55,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,难道是因为青椒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:13.75,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我觉得你是因为早上吃了讨厌的东西才会心情不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.82,0:04:16.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,她怎么知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:19.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,青椒确实很苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:24.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,难道说  高木同学你讨厌青椒？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.84,0:04:27.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,还有一股涩味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:29.83,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:34.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就是呀  为什么要一大早吃青椒呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:36.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我倒是不讨厌青椒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:42.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,原来西片你讨厌青椒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:46.70,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你的口味真像小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:48.63,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,被她耍了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:52.86,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那高木同学你没有讨厌的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.59,0:04:54.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,讨厌的东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.18,0:04:59.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不好说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:01.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,看来她一定有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.85,0:05:06.18,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,如果猜出高木同学讨厌的东西就算我赢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:09.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可以啊  虽然我觉得你猜不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:14.23,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我一定要猜出来  然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:18.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,「真是小孩的口味」这样说她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:22.70,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我说  不知道用什么emoji表情时超苦恼的对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:25.83,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,一种蔬菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.52,0:05:27.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,原来你想要提示啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:32.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不是蔬菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:35.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,还有  这是一种能让人振奋精神的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.38,0:05:37.99,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什么味道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:41.86,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,很清爽  酸中带甜？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:43.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.60,0:05:47.19,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,等一下  只能再给你一个提示
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.58,0:05:51.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,要是提示没有次数限制  你迟早能猜到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.38,0:05:56.58,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不愧是高木同学  我的气势被阻停了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.81,0:06:00.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,还有一次  能确定的提示
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.14,0:06:03.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什么颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.62,0:06:07.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,黄色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.15,0:06:09.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.46,0:06:11.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,范围大大缩小了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:12.71,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.01,0:06:20.74,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就是它了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:28.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学讨厌的东西是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.90,0:06:31.18,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,菠萝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:31.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.90,0:06:32.54,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这么快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.68,0:06:40.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我多问一句  答案是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:44.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,能量饮料一类的饮品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.54,0:06:46.23,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这哪里是吃的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:49.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你问我的可是我讨厌的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:52.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,而且  我说了「不好说」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:57.65,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你是说过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:06:58.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:05.32,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.06,0:07:09.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,如果我给西片做饭的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.50,0:07:13.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,如果…那种事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:17.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,说不定会有那么一天哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.60,0:07:23.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那时候我一定会给你做出好吃的青椒料理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:25.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:27.59,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,啊  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.60,0:07:29.83,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我们去拿讲义吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.24,0:07:30.80,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:35.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,说起来昨天买的书  超级有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.82,0:07:38.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,拜托你不要放青椒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:43.40,Takagi san—Picture 05-2,,0,0,0,,{\frz272\pos(122.333,517.333)}{\fad(330,400)}饺子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:44.48,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,喂  美奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:46.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,能帮我把胡萝卜吃掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.14,0:07:47.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.06,0:07:52.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,友加里你又挑食了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:55.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这样的话长不高的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.53,0:07:58.80,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,现在比你高就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.34,0:08:02.30,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,作为交换  给你饺子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:06.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不用啦  只是麻烦你帮我把讨厌的东西吃掉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:08.91,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,没事  我喜欢胡萝卜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.12,0:08:11.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但是美奈你也喜欢饺子对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.61,0:08:13.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我什么都喜欢  没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:15.76,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.78,0:08:17.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:19.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我还是不能要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.41,0:08:20.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,来来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:21.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不用不用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.11,0:08:22.55,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,给你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.58,0:08:24.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,都说了不能要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:25.27,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.95,0:08:32.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这个饺子好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.96,0:08:35.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,早苗你干嘛吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.13,0:08:37.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就是  你干嘛吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.06,0:08:40.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,因为你俩都不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.34,0:08:43.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我没那么说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.68,0:08:46.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,早苗  快点道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.39,0:08:54.07,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,早苗  你去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.01,0:09:05.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,木村  这都第几个了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.33,0:09:11.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,为了明天的会议  现在要补充营养
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:14.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,要决定文化祭的节目是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.60,0:09:15.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.72,0:09:20.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,大家在犹豫要不要做铃铛蛋糕套圈  但我想搞炸鸡  咖啡厅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.88,0:09:22.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,炸鸡  咖啡厅？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:25.19,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,月本同学同意了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.98,0:09:33.18,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,她同不同意无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.85,0:09:40.23,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,文化祭委员里  实际上几乎只有我一个人在干活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:46.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不管别人怎么说  节目必须是炸鸡  咖啡厅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.59,0:09:44.92,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}木村…喂  木村
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.78,0:09:47.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,后面  后面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.22,0:09:51.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,月本同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:55.62,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不  那个  西片他们也赞成…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:09:57.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,别把我们卷进去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:05.87,Takagi san—Picture 05-3,,0,0,0,,{\frz270.1\pos(1092,518)}{\fad(450,0)}菠萝包
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:05.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.92,0:10:07.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.18,0:10:10.50,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,原来你不是不想吃饺子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:12.47,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.32,0:10:16.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什么嘛  早苗也有温柔的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.62,0:10:19.76,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,所以  用你剩下的饺子和菠萝包交换吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.13,0:10:24.07,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,差不多得了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:32.82,Takagi san—Picture 05-4,,0,0,0,,{\frz270.1\pos(330.666,336)}{\fad(300,300)}炸鸡  咖啡厅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.33,0:10:32.78,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,根据投票结果  我们班的节目就决定是我们提议的话剧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:34.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,太好了  友加里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.64,0:10:37.83,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,总之  剧本由我负责
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:38.11,Takagi san—Picture 05-5,,0,0,0,,{\frz270.1\pos(92,412)}{\fad(400,360)}分配角色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:41.70,Takagi san—Picture 05-6,,0,0,0,,{\frz269.1\pos(862,186)}话剧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:41.70,Takagi san—Picture 05-6,,0,0,0,,{\pos(994,134)\frz271.3}答题大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:41.70,Takagi san—Picture 05-6,,0,0,0,,{\s0\pos(1224,146)\frz270.9\u0}鬼屋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:41.70,Takagi san—Picture 05-7,,0,0,0,,{\p1\fscx626\fscy643\pos(1238,294)}m 0 0 l 0 -15 l 1 -15 l 1 0 l 0 0
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:41.70,Takagi san—Picture 05-6,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1174,140)\frz271.6}有其他班级做了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:41.70,Takagi san—Picture 05-6,,0,0,0,,{\frz270.6\pos(1300,204)}炒素面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:41.70,Takagi san—Picture 05-6,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(1422,178)}香草茶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.97,0:10:39.19,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,导演是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.40,0:10:41.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,服装由我负责
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.09,0:10:43.09,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.84,0:10:45.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎…怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:47.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我就知道会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:50.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,从来没听过什么炸鸡  咖啡厅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:52.58,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片投的哪个节目
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:55.39,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是最喜欢的炸鸡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:58.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我只是受木村之托而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:11:02.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,老师  考虑到正式演出前的日程安排
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.50,0:11:07.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我想今天就确定演员  下次就开始彩排  可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.90,0:11:09.70,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,话剧的内容定了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.96,0:11:11.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.72,0:11:15.78,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,简单来说  就是公主和王子的爱情故事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.58,0:11:18.09,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是我们三个人想出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.57,0:11:20.79,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,很有意思哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:24.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,很久很久以前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.84,0:11:30.27,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,某个地方  有位被诅咒变成青蛙的王子名叫朱丽夫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.03,0:11:34.92,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,他一直躲避着人们的视线  藏身于森林里的城堡里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:40.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,有一天  他和误闯到此的公主罗密代命运般地邂逅了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:42.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,两人很快坠入爱河
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.12,0:11:43.91,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但是  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:48.85,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,企图拆散两人的黑魔法师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.37,0:11:51.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,逃亡的朱丽夫和罗密代
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.42,0:11:55.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,前来拯救两人的帅气伙伴们  这个是我的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:59.65,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,然后是既悲伤又令人感动的最后一幕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.94,0:12:00.50,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:03.99,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,两人的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:06.30,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,究竟会如何上演呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:07.98,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.28,0:12:08.98,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,会打败魔女吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:09.78,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.05,0:12:10.58,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,反派…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.22,0:12:13.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,黑魔法师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.21,0:12:13.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}炸鸡咖啡厅…炸鸡咖啡厅…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:18.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,太好了  大家似乎都很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:21.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,然后是选角
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.42,0:12:24.30,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学比较适合公主的形象吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:27.53,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,头发又长又顺滑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:29.75,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,整个人的气质又很文静
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:31.54,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我想选高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.24,0:12:32.70,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.32,0:12:36.48,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,大家怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:38.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不错嘛  赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.81,0:12:41.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学…演公主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.62,0:12:45.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.36,0:12:49.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,大家觉得没问题的话我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.64,0:12:52.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那公主的角色就定了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:54.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.06,0:12:57.97,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,问题是演对手戏的青蛙王子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:00.58,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我们一直定不了人选
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.93,0:13:01.53,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.58,0:13:03.81,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我们来试镜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:05.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,试镜？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.83,0:13:06.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.77,0:13:09.81,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,男生们逐个来高木同学面前表演
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.94,0:13:12.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,选出最有王子范儿的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.09,0:13:15.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,简直就是反串版灰姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.62,0:13:17.75,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,寻找命中注定之人的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.16,0:13:20.30,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真令人心动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:23.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片  来比赛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:29.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,要是西片被选上演王子  就算你赢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:29.85,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:32.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学  可以请你上来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.73,0:13:32.97,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.22,0:13:35.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这什么比赛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.63,0:13:39.18,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,哦  我心爱的罗密代公主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:40.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,果然是那样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:40.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,下一位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.49,0:13:45.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,哦  我心爱的罗密代公主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.90,0:13:46.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,下一位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:49.50,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,哦  呱呱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:50.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,下一位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:53.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你是演黑魔法使的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.57,0:13:55.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:13:58.07,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,比赛就是比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.33,0:14:02.55,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,一定要选上王子角色  让高木同学无言以对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.74,0:14:05.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,大家完全没有融入感情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.50,0:14:08.48,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,多展现出对公主的爱意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:11.09,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这是比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.13,0:14:11.80,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,下一位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.46,0:14:14.84,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片同学你有听到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:27.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.74,0:14:30.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,有那味儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.21,0:14:31.81,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:34.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,果然这两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.06,0:14:37.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好让我心动加速啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.33,0:14:39.50,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我心爱的炸鸡…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:42.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么了  王子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:43.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我心爱的炸鸡…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.18,0:14:44.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可恶的高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:47.83,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,她肯定以为我会害羞得说不出口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.39,0:14:49.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这就说给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:54.62,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,哦  我…我心…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.94,0:14:56.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我心爱的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:09.55,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我心爱的炸鸡  好想吃掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.00,0:15:10.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.57,0:15:12.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,刚才那句
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.57,0:15:14.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,把「炸鸡」换成「公主」再说一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:17.87,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我心爱的公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.34,0:15:19.76,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,决定是他了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:22.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,能感受到他迸发的爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:24.63,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,木村来演王子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:28.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但是  他又没多少青蛙王子的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:31.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我觉得西片同学来比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.52,0:15:33.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这样啊  确实
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:36.48,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但还是木村好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.09,0:15:38.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,换成猪猪王子来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.28,0:15:41.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,猪猪王子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.38,0:15:41.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}算了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:46.53,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,虽然今天你们的选角进展顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.03,0:15:51.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但要想办好文化祭  最重要的是班级要团结一心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:54.97,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,每个人都要把自己当成主角  互相协作…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:54.60,Takagi san—Picture 05-6,,0,0,0,,{\frz269.8\fs80\pos(1120,426)}{\fad(450,450)}吉备团子  西片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:57.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真可惜呢西片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.33,0:15:59.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,演的角色跟王子就差一个字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:02.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,「王子」跟「团子」完全不一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:04.76,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,说起来演吉备团子是闹哪样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:06.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但真遗憾呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.51,0:16:10.75,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我还想听西片饱含爱意的话语呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.35,0:16:12.80,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那只是台词罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:14.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,喂  西片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.89,0:16:16.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.62,0:16:33.55,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,还有多远啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:35.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就快到了  高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.50,0:16:42.78,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你想到没有人烟的地方干什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.84,0:16:44.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,吉备团子A同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:45.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:48.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,要把饱含爱意的话语说完吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:51.32,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,都说是比赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:57.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,看  到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:16:59.27,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,池塘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:04.00,Takagi san—Picture 05-8,,0,0,0,,{\frz271.1\pos(1410,316)}{\fad(450,500)}钓鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:03.80,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,诶  这种地方还有池塘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:08.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是木村告诉我的秘密场所
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.45,0:17:10.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,然后这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.72,0:17:12.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,钓竿和钓饵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.12,0:17:14.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,今天是钓鱼比赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.86,0:17:15.78,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:20.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,先在这个池塘里钓上5条鲫鱼的人获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:22.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:26.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片似乎起了个大早
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.82,0:17:29.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,特意为我做的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.77,0:17:34.32,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那就开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.69,0:17:34.87,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:37.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,预备  开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.74,0:17:50.97,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,悠闲自在的感觉真好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:17:59.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯  说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:02.98,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我说啊  这个池塘里有大鱼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.45,0:18:04.55,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,大鱼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.72,0:18:08.98,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,据木村所说  是有条大家伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.62,0:18:15.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我说啊  钓上它的人无条件获胜如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.12,0:18:17.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,行是行  但我觉得不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.12,0:18:20.53,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,对新手高木同学来说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:24.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我觉得还是专注钓上第一条比较好…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.92,0:18:28.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,太好了  第一条
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.55,0:18:29.18,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.34,0:18:32.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,被抢先了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:35.59,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,惩罚游戏要你做什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.66,0:18:38.85,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你也就能得瑟这一会儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.24,0:18:42.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你能把那条鱼的鱼钩取下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.25,0:18:45.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,取不下就无法钓下一条
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.94,0:18:48.47,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这样下去就是我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.92,0:18:53.59,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那么  继续继续
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.47,0:18:56.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.88,0:19:06.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我在家有处理过鱼  所以没问题哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.17,0:19:08.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真遗憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.69,0:19:09.78,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.81,0:19:11.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但她还只钓了一条
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.86,0:19:13.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,比赛才刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.58,0:19:16.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,第二条
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.64,0:19:22.58,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学你以前没钓过鱼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.92,0:19:25.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯  应该是新手运气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.39,0:19:28.87,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,冷静点  新手终究是新手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:31.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,运气不可能一直持续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.34,0:19:34.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我马上就反超
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.59,0:19:36.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,上钩了哦西片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:46.74,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,哇  好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.09,0:19:49.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这是  那条大家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:27.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.17,0:20:29.86,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但幸亏你没掉进水里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.81,0:20:40.58,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片的鱼线都断了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:42.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,算我赢可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.54,0:20:44.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.29,0:20:46.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.88,0:20:52.07,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,心脏狂跳不止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.97,0:20:54.97,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.71,0:20:57.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,Koi
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.71,0:20:57.04,Takagi san—Picture 05-9,,0,0,0,,恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.84,0:21:08.09,Takagi san—Picture 05-9,,0,0,0,,{\pos(822,1000)}Koi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.84,0:21:08.09,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是鲤鱼呢  那条大鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.89,0:21:18.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,啊…说的是鱼对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.95,0:21:28.85,Takagi san—Picture 05-9,,0,0,0,,{\pos(958,1000)}恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.95,0:21:28.85,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真想跟鲤鱼道谢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.59,0:21:30.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.69,0:21:34.32,Takagi san—Picture 05-9,,0,0,0,,{\pos(852,996)}恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.69,0:21:34.32,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,多亏了鲤鱼  我才赢了西片
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.76,0:21:40.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,该让你做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:42.71,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可恶的高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.95,0:21:45.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,对了  文化祭话剧的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.23,0:21:47.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你陪我一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.82,0:21:49.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.92,0:21:51.19,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,用跟王子差一个字的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.14,0:21:54.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,团子角色来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.66,0:21:59.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可以  毕竟我输了比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.98,0:22:11.12,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}どうして君が泣くの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.25,0:22:16.97,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}まだ僕も泣いていないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.10,0:22:23.28,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}自分より  悲しむから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.43,0:22:30.57,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}つらいのがどっちか  わからなくなるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.77,0:22:38.39,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}ガラクタだったはずの今日が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.65,0:22:45.81,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}ふたりなら  宝物になる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.90,0:22:49.21,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}そばにいたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.27,0:22:58.71,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}君のために出来ることが  僕にあるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.90,0:23:10.30,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}いつも君に  ずっと君に  笑っていてほしくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:22.95,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}ひまわりのような  まっすぐなその優しさを  温もりを全部
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.19,0:23:29.29,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}これからは僕も 届けて行きたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.34,0:23:37.44,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}ここにある幸せに 気づいたから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.98,0:22:11.12,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}你为何会哭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.25,0:22:16.97,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}明明我还未落泪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.10,0:22:23.28,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}是比我更悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.43,0:22:30.57,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}还是更加痛苦  我已搞不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.77,0:22:38.39,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}本是破铜烂铁的今天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.65,0:22:45.81,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}两人一起的话  就将成为宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.90,0:22:49.21,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}想待在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.27,0:22:58.71,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}我能否为你做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.90,0:23:10.30,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}想让你一直笑  想要你永远笑下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:22.95,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}今后我也想想将向日葵般  那直率的温柔和温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.19,0:23:29.29,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}全部送到你心里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.34,0:23:37.44,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}因为察觉到了幸福就在此处
